# thetacog-mcp — standalone public repo.
# This repo is SELF-CONTAINED: `git clone` + `npm i` + `npx thetacog-mcp attest-demo`
# runs with no monorepo access (clean-room verified). The prebuilt on-chip daemon,
# reef data, walk driver, and book all ship. Exclude only build artifacts + deps:
node_modules/
pmu-rust/target/          # 57M Rust build tree — the daemon ships prebuilt under .thetacog/pmu/target/release/
.DS_Store
*.log
npm-debug.log*
.env
.env.*
